i owned an '05 tl for 6.5 years/85k trouble-free, fun and efficient miles. one of honda/acuras best designs imo (along with original acura coupe). clean, elegant, sporty. i was so disheartened by the current design, did not consider it for even a moment. the toned down beak/shield is an improvement, but still wouldn't mind seeing it go the way of the dodos... the tlx, from appearances, welcome back, acura!
